00:00:00,640 --> 00:00:06,080
Heritor Newsflash! This is an urgent broadcast! I repeat — this is an urgent broadcast!

2
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:16,920
News has finally emerged regarding the attack on Madam Herta! The Annihilation Gang has claimed responsibility for the incident and warned of further activity. The Guild has expressed utmost condemnation...

3
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:27,520
The gods of the starry skies have abandoned the world — they give no thought to the masses.

4
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:36,280
Only the wounded savior can bathe the world in the firelight of Destruction.

5
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:46,320
Yet always there are cowards trying in vain to reject their favor and escape the wounds.

6
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:59,120
Flee, then. Flee as far as you can! No matter the distance, annihilation will find you!

